code: @Override public LocalProperties computeLocalProperties(LocalProperties in1, LocalProperties in2) {     // uniqueness becomes grouping with streamed nested loops     if ((in2.getGroupedFields() == null || in2.getGroupedFields().size() == 0) && in2.getUniqueFields() != null && in2.getUniqueFields().size() > 0) {         return LocalProperties.forGrouping(in2.getUniqueFields().iterator().next().toFieldList()).     } else {         return in2.clearUniqueFieldSets().     } }
